        {"label": "C", "content": "12"},
        {"label": "D", "content": "16"}
      ],
      "correct": "B",
      "explanation": "4^(3/2) = (4^(1/2))³ = 2³ = 8."
    },
    {
      "order": 6, "code": "MATH-006", "topic": "Logarithm",
